<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Lany indray ny andro FFPM720</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lany indray ny andro ;
 Hianao ry Ray,
 No ho masoandro
 Sy ampinganay.

[V2]
 Be ny zava-tsoa
 Azo taminao ;
 Saotra aman-dera
 Entinay izao.

[V3]
 Andronay mandalo
 Toy ny rivotra ;
 Be ny fahavalo
 Mampitahotra.

[V4]
 Jeso ô, Mpiandry,
 Izaho ondrinao,
 Aoka re mba handry
 Eo an-tratranao.

[V5]
 Mpivahiny ihany
 Izahay atý,
 Ka mba te-ho any
 Aminao arý.</lyrics>
